BAIL HEARING - 
Defendant in custody and appearing by video from the Manitowoc County Jail.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of resist officer causing soft tissue injury.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 08-08-22 at 1:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $1,000.00 recognizance bond with the conditions that defendant is to have no contact with any establishment whose primary sales are alcoholic beverages and defendant must maintain absolute sobriety.   Bail furnished and defendant is released from custody.
